.container-fluid.bg-dark
  .row
    .col-md-6.height-full.left-col
      .cols
        %h1 My Awesome Project #1
        %br
        %p Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vestibulum vehicula sem sit amet risus pellentesque, at facilisis ipsum euismod. Aliquam interdum pharetra diam et imperdiet. 
        %br
        Vestibulum placerat arcu lectus, ut suscipit nisi maximus ac. In hac habitasse platea dictumst. Nulla eros urna, condimentum ac suscipit at, mollis sit amet metus. Aliquam vitae tristique lectus, a eleifend lorem. Suspendisse potenti. Nulla facilisi. Morbi sollicitudin egestas molestie. Duis non lectus pulvinar, ultricies sem sit amet, blandit eros.
    .col-md-6.height-full.right
      .cols
        = partial 'partials/_come-at-me'
.container-fluid.middle
  .container.my-other-projects
    %h3 Some of my other projects
    %br
    .row
      - data.projects.each do |project|
        .col-md-4
          .card.mb-4.box-shadow
            %img.card-img-top{:alt => "Thumbnail [100%x225]", "data-holder-rendered" => "true", "data-src" => "holder.js/100px225?theme=thumb&bg=55595c&fg=eceeef&text=Thumbnail", :src => "/images/#{project[:coverimage]}.png", :style => "height: 225px; width: 100%; display: block;"}/
            .card-body
              %p.card-text This is a wider card with supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content. This content is a little bit longer.
              .d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center
                .btn-group
                  %button.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary{:type => "button"} View
                  %button.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary{:type => "button"} Edit
                %small.text-muted 9 mins
